process, at which point you may be able to share comments, photos, and location
information with other users as you choose.</p>

<p>We require you to read the privacy policies of the social
networking services that you use. You have the ability to disconnect from such
social networking services at any time by signing out of the service within the
4<sup>th</sup> & Mayor application, or uninstalling the app from your
phone.</p>

